n, Help Me!</span><br>  Posts: 1249<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 9:28 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Q about tomorrow's patch</span><hr size=1> I'd assume the level limit to be exactly the same as the one that doesn't allow you to cast high level buffs on lower level people directly. That would be 45 I think? Correct me if I'm wrong, it's been a while <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
You were never able to cast high level buffs on lower level people. The workaround was using a group spell and targetting someone higher level. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=68571" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://images.crimsontempest.info/yaxa/yaxsig31.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.crimsontempest.info" target="top">Crimson Tempest</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=seaotter42>SeaOtter42</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 307<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 9:52 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Q about tomorrow's patch</span><hr size=1> on the test server they'd &quot;fixed&quot; it so that group spells checked for the level limit too. I dont know if it will go in... I hope not... I rather enjoy playing my twink shaman with KEI.<br>
<br>
 <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=269910"><img src="http://www.geocities.com/jeremy_moffitt/images/ottersig1.jpg"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lordbug>LordBug</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 763<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 9:58 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Q about tomorrow's patch</span><hr size=1> Level 51+ buffs only land on level 46+ people.<br>
