Morgan Le Fay</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pickkpockket999>Pickk Pockket999</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 166<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 10:20 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Q about tomorrow's patch</span><hr size=1> I hope bard AoE songs are not effected. I'm powerleveling myself up a little froglok wizard atm and I've hit 34 with him without ever getting a KEI. But if manasong doesn't land I will be seriously upset. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=khalensilverthorn>KhalenSilverThorn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 10:56 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Q about tomorrow's patch</span><hr size=1> If it goes in like it on Test... <br>
<br>
<br>
Not even higher level evacs touch lower level characters... so I doubt they &quot;forgot&quot; bards.  No heals above 50 land on sub46 chars.  No buffs.... no nothing.<br>
